      "date": "2013-01-10 03:13:19.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/90c274f2-5acf-11e2-84d3-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
